title: North West Tries to Paint Her Bedroom Walls With Purple Nail Polish
text: North West Tries to Paint Her Bedroom Walls With Purple Nail Polish Most Popular By Alyssa Bailey Feb 7, 2017 Child prodigy North West found a new use for her purple nail polish while her mother was out of the room: paint for her bedroom wall. This didn't work out so well, Kim Kardashian showed on Snapchat: A video posted by Kim Kardashian Snapchats (@kimksnapchats) on Feb 7, 2017 at 9:06am PST Advertisement - Continue Reading Below But! North did damage control by giving her mom plenty of paper towels to clean up with. Redemption never looked so cute: A video posted by Kim Kardashian Snapchats (@kimksnapchats) on Feb 7, 2017 at 9:11am PST More from ELLE:
